room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Tactical Escape 101 in Eau Claire
room_description: Iit’s been 23 hours since the call came in. You’ve received your ransom demands and they include stealing eight items from the top Drug Lord’s personal bank. From the outside it looks like such a harmless place but you’ll need some help. Good thing your friend works for the bank. It’ll be easier now that it’s an INSIDE JOB!
